org.osgi.service.cdi.annotations

Annotation Type ReferenceFilter


  • @Target(value=ANNOTATION_TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
public @interface ReferenceFilter
    Annotation applied to Qualifier for use on Reference for conversion to service filters. The qualifier is converted to Map following the rules defined by the converter specification along with name mangling. The key/value pairs are then 'ANDed' together. Multiple such Qualifiers' on a single Reference are 'ANDed' together and as such can be combined.
